Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:04.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,空が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:06.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,灰色だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:10.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何だか知らない街みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,迷っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:20.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お母さんの前で　私は泣かない子供だった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:24.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,これからも絶対泣かないと決めていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お父さんが出ていって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私が泣くべき分もお母さんは悲しんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:37.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さみしさは与えられていたものが奪われたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,初めて感じるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:44.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,初めから与えられなかった者は　それすら分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ずっと心地よくすらあった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,独りの世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:51.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.23,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.71,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたが色を添える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よかった　花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:03.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,捜したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:08.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お母さんから「花ちゃんがいなくなった」って連絡が来て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さっ　帰ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:14.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:24.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,急に恥ずかしくなった　強がっていた自分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:31.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうして　温かい場所をくれたあなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:34.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,また私を独りにするの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:48.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃんの髪はさらさら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,斜め分けの前髪だって似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火　起きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:57.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.59,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おはよう　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:09.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.87,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あのさ　俺さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントは全部知ってんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そこまでバカじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:07.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でもあいつに言ったって　絶対理解されねえし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ていうか　むしろ嫌われ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.63,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺　あいつに嫌われたくなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.35,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,本当に分かんないときもあったさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なんてこと言うんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,茜さんにかぎって　そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.67,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かんないの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦は子供だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ほーらね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんな　おっさんと…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:59.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありゃあ大学の教授とみた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その日一晩泣きぬれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも次の日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめーん　遅れちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.47,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,茜さんは平然と家庭教師として来て
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ケーキ食べる？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:16.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,買ってきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,うげ　昨日と同じ服だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その角度カワイイと思ってやってるな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,この人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,男がいないと生きていけないんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何だか　そう思うと今度は急に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:40.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,茜さんは弱くてかわいそうな女の人に思えた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:45.23,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦ちゃん　クリーム付いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,吐きそう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ラブホのシャンプーのにおいなんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なめる？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いや　いいです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,この女ぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも　何だかそれから俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あっ　シャーペン落としちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,んしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,計算か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:26.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,浅はかさすら計算なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:32.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何だかさらに虜になってしまったのである
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そこがいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.23,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,痛っ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今思えば嫉妬かな　先輩なりの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,きっとあいつだったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あり得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,見る目なさ過ぎ　死んで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でもそういう素直なとこ　嫌いじゃないな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:19.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今日は土曜　俺は暇だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,来てくれると思いませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:42.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.15,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺の思春期　どうにかしてください
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,時間もったいないから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホテル行こっか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,や…あの　そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんなつもりで呼んだんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいよ　私にも責任あるしね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっとあの…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,責任感とかでしてもらわなくても　別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,したいでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:22.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そりゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.07,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あのね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:43.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦の都合でしたことってなかったの　知ってた？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だからこれでチャラね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,先輩はそのまま　泊まらずに帰った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.11,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ねえ　麦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:10.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:14.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.95,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あっつー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,夏休みだね　もうすぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,うち進学クラスじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,課題量ヤバいらしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私と麦はあるときすごく近かった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,気のせいじゃなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でもまた　こんなに他人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,２人きりでいる時間が減った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:55.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あまり核心に触れる話をしなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:59.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんが告白したことも　結局言わずじまいで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:05.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お互い何となく　隠し事が増えたことを察した上で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,問いかける手間さえ回避しようとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私はもうえっちゃんでいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだよ　さみしさを埋めるだけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦はもう必要ないや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.23,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう　いらない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦　他の人としたでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,しただろ　花火も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.23,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.35,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かるよ　だって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何よ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいよ　たぶん同じだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すげえ　気持ちよくなってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦も…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:38.67,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ねえ　何で　苦しいの嫌なの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.27,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でもね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:42.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あのね…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すごく気持ちいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.51,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私と麦はよく似てるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ろくでもないところが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:03.87,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,日々は淡々と誰の上にも平等にあるものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:08.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,毎日が退屈かどうか　全て自分しだい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,チャイムの音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:21.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,チャイム　時間割　登校時間　下校時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,放課後　早寝　早起き
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,時間は区切らなきゃ目に見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ここは　縛られてばかりね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.74,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あ…あの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私が一番欲しているもの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,日常から連れ出してくれる絶対的何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,「自由」よ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.40,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺んちに来るの久しぶりじゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:13.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ああ　うん　久しぶり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:16.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何照れてんの　バーカ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:20.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,バ…バカ…じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何かそう　それ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よくするね　その目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おびえてるのに　怖いのに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,真っすぐにじっと俺を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,奇麗な人だな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.59,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,めちゃくちゃにどろどろに汚したい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:50.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺は男だから　そういうもんだって分かってたって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やるせなく　悲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.11,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦　しよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺だって　本当は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:07.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大事に大事に閉じ込めてしまっておきたいものだってあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,返事を…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.99,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,してませんでしたよね　まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,は…はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.48,UP JP,,0,0,0,,それで　えっとね　えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私に言わせんな　つまんない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それで…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.31,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,正直
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:34.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まだお互いのこと　よく知らないじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから取りあえず　えーと…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,鐘井先生　今晩お時間あったり…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,残念でしょうがない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もっとさぁ　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,頑張ってほしいんれふよぉ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:06.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,は…はあ　生徒さんにですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,むしゃくしゃしてたから酔っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:20.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,しまった　こんなに飲むつもりじゃなかったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:24.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だって　つまんないんだもん　こいつが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,本当に飲まないんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,は…はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,弱いんです　すっごく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,つまんないことは最初から分かってたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,思った以上につまんなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私　つまんないだけの存在ってホント嫌い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ま…待ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まだ　返事を…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,返事って…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.55,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから　ぼ…僕と…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だ…大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:10.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すいません　つい　癖で…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何でこんなときに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.27,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,前言撤回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:35.07,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,つまんない今日は　楽しい今日に変わるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,スイッチ入った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,消えかけのキスマーク
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,バ…バカ　やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:58.83,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:03.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺とのキスマーク　誰かに見られたら困る？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その代わり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今日は最後までして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.75,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いやいや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ルール違反じゃん　それ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,出たよ　ヒステリック　気まぐれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,妄言　自己中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:26.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,付き合いきれねぇ　ホント　マジで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,結局ホテル？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.51,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.40,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えーと…　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ああ　行った行った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一応申し訳程度に夜景見たわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ここは　僕の取って置きのお気に入りスポットで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.79,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,で　結局これね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,い…いいんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,了承？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ここに来て了承取るの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントどこがいいの　花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:10.99,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,Ｃ組の安楽岡さんって子　カワイイですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:15.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ずいぶん鐘井先生と仲がいいみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,は…花…　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:20.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,安楽岡さんは小さいころから家が近所で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,きょうだい同然に育ったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か特別扱いしているように見えたなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違うんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:35.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おかしいかな　そんな子に嫉妬なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ちょろ過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:55.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,痛…痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:56.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,痛い痛い　無理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:02.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,冷えちゃったね　体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,風邪ひくから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.83,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何でできないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,「何で」って…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,別に俺のこと好きじゃないからだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,「じゃあ」って何だよ「じゃあ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんなにやりたいのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,見てらんないよ　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なあ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺とちゃんと付き合う？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あっ　ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お前ってまだ処女？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントに帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:31.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,独り
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,独りは嫌だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,独りって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何だか空っぽなの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:49.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰かと一緒に眠りたい…なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:55.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私はなんて弱くなってしまったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:07.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,昨日　鐘井先生と…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,しちゃった
Comment: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,----------TEXT_CN----------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.48,0:00:04.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.69,0:00:06.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是灰色的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.97,0:00:10.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,眼前的城市好陌生
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我迷路了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.04,0:00:20.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,在妈妈面前 我从来不哭
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.18,0:00:24.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我暗自决定以后也绝对不哭
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,爸爸离开家之后
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,妈妈把我该流的泪都流干了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.48,0:00:37.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,人在得到的东西被夺走的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,才会感到寂寞
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.30,0:00:44.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,如果一开始就不曾拥有 又怎么能懂得寂寞
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,甚至还会一直享受
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一个人的世界
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.90,0:00:51.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.23,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.71,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你给世界添上了色彩
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,太好了 小花
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:03.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,找你半天了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.48,0:01:08.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你妈妈之前打电话跟我说你不见了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,来 回去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.95,0:01:14.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.71,0:01:24.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我突然为自己的逞强感到羞愧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.36,0:01:31.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么 你曾经给予我温暖
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.12,0:01:34.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在又让我孤独一人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.22,0:01:48.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小绘的头发好柔顺
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,偏分刘海也很适合她
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火 醒了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.00,0:01:57.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.59,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.90,0:02:09.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.87,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,告诉你 我啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.58,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其实什么都知道
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还没有那么笨
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.02,0:04:07.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过就算跟她说了也得不到理解
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,反而会遭到嫌弃…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.63,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我竟然还怕被她嫌弃吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.35,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,说真的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也有过看不透的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你怎么说话呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,茜姐她 绝对不是那种人…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.67,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这都看不出来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.38,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦真是幼稚啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,看到没有
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,竟然跟 那种大叔…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.47,0:04:59.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,目测是大学教授
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那天我哭了一整夜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但第二天
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.47,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,茜姐还是若无其事地来做家教
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要吃蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.64,0:05:16.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我顺路买来的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.16,0:05:20.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我去 是昨天那套衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这个角度肯定是在装可爱给我看
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她这种人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要是离开男人就活不下去了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这么一想 我突然觉得
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.65,0:05:40.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,茜姐真是个既柔弱又可怜的女人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.93,0:05:45.23,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小麦 你嘴边沾着奶油哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好想吐
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,情人旅馆的洗发水味吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要舔吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这个女人…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过 在那之后我似乎…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,啊 我把自动铅弄掉了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,算计我
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.66,0:06:26.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,连我有多肤浅都算准了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.46,0:06:32.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,似乎反而对她更加着迷了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你喜欢她那样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.23,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在想来 学姐是嫉妒了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要是那家伙 肯定会…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有病啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,太没眼光了 去死吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过我倒也不讨厌她的直率
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.56,0:07:19.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,今天周六 我很闲
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.58,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没想到你真的会来
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.21,0:07:42.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,找我干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.15,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,请拯救下我的青春期
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别浪费时间了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,去开房吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不…那个 我不是…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你找我不就是为了这事吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没关系 我也有责任
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其实 你不必出于责任感跟我做的…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你想做吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.61,0:08:22.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有点…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.07,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.50,0:08:43.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,知道吗 以前你都没有主动要求过
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以这算是扯平了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,学姐没留下过夜 就这么回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.11,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喂 麦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.85,0:09:10.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.76,0:09:14.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.95,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就快放暑假了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们不是毕业班吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,据说作业超级多
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我和麦曾经走得很近
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那不是错觉
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但现在 又疏远了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,两人独处的时间变少了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.04,0:09:55.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,话题也开始变得无关痛痒了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.81,0:09:59.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,结果我还是没把哥哥表白的事告诉他
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.92,0:10:05.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们不但隐约察觉到彼此的秘密变多了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还连问都不愿意问起
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我只要有小绘就够了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊 为了排解寂寞的话
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就没有必要找麦了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.23,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不需要了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦 你和别人做过了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你不也做了吗 花火
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.23,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,做了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.35,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我猜到了 因为…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别说了 我们想的大概一样
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.89,0:11:26.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得 特别有感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你也是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.84,0:11:38.67,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么 明明很痛苦 很抗拒
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.27,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.92,0:11:42.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就觉得…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,特别有感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.51,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我和麦真的很像
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都不是什么好东西
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.09,0:12:03.87,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,时间面前 人人平等
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.50,0:12:08.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,每天过得是否无聊 全在于自己
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,铃声响了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.65,0:12:21.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,打铃 课程表 到校时间 离校时间
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,放学后 早睡 早起
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,时间只有被分割 才能看得见
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这里到处都是束缚啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.74,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我最渴望的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是能带我摆脱乏味生活的救星…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,即「自由」
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.40,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你好久没来过我家了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.88,0:13:13.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊 好久没来了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.36,0:13:16.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,害羞什么呢 笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.84,0:13:20.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,才…才不是…笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没错 就是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她总是露出这种眼神
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,明明在恐惧 在害怕
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还非要目不转睛地看着我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,多美的人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.59,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好想肆意玷污蹂躏
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.66,0:13:50.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,即便知道自己身为男人 天性如此
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还是不禁感到悲哀
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.11,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦 来做吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别看我这样
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.73,0:14:07.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其实我也有想要好好珍藏的东西啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.99,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没有给你回复呢 对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.48,UP CN,,0,0,0,,那么 怎么说呢 那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别让我来说啊 真无趣
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.31,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.35,0:14:34.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们对彼此 还不太了解吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以目前就先 让我想想啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,钟井老师 今晚有空吗…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,扫兴得要命
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就不能再给力一点吗…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.53,0:15:06.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我…我懂了 你是指学生吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一闹心就把自己灌醉了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.34,0:15:20.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,糟糕 我本来没打算喝这么多的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.08,0:15:24.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都怪这家伙 他太无趣了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你真的不喝酒吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我酒量特别差
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,虽然一开始就知道会很无趣
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没想到能这么无趣
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我讨厌死这种无趣透顶的人了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,请…请等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你还没回复我…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,什么回复…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.55,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就是说 和…和我…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.13,0:16:10.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.58,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我说惯了…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么偏在这种时候…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.27,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,当我没说
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.70,0:16:35.07,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,无趣的今天 也许要变得有趣起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,进入状态
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,快要消失的吻痕
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,笨…笨蛋 别这样
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.01,0:16:58.83,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.18,0:17:03.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你怕别人看到我留下的吻痕吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,作为补偿
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,今天做到最后吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.75,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那样就违背约定了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,开始了 歇斯底里 反复无常
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,胡言乱语 自私自利
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.46,0:17:26.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我受不了这种人 说实话 真心的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,果然来开房了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.51,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.40,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对了 去了那里
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,陪他随便看了看夜景
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.60,0:17:49.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这里 轻易不带别人来的…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.79,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,绕了一圈还是开房
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可…可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,征求同意？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,来都来了 还用问吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花 你到底看上他什么了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.99,0:18:10.99,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,C班的安乐冈同学 真的好可爱啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.14,0:18:15.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,感觉她和你关系特别好
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小…小…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.13,0:18:20.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学从小就住在我家附近
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们一起长大 就像兄妹一样
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得我偏向她的话…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.08,0:18:35.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,说来也怪 我居然嫉妒那孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,轻松拿下
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.00,0:18:55.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,疼…好疼
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.02,0:18:56.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼 不行了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.84,0:19:02.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你身体都变凉了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.83,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么做不成啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,大概是因为你不喜欢我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那就当我喜欢你
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,什么叫就当你喜欢我啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你就这么想做吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我都看不下去了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,正式跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你还是处女吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我真要回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.91,0:20:31.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我讨厌一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一个人待着
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,总觉得很空虚
